<item>
            <title>[SOLR-12750] Migrate API should lock the collection instead of shard</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-12750</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The Migrate API acquires the lock at the shard level and not even all of the relevant ones because the API can affect many shards and that information is not available at the time when the locking decisions are made. It is best if the Migrate API locks the entire collection instead of shard.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
